        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Volume of Cu in casted alloys is estimated to 6% of global Cu consumption, 90% of this being brass, based on global shares reported in Joseph G (1999) Copper: its trade, manufacture, use, and environmental status. Materials Park: ASM International. 70% Cu content in brass.</productionVolumeComment>
